{"id":23,"date":"2015-10-03T10:32:17","date_gmt":"2015-10-03T10:32:17","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.monstereventhire.co.uk\/?page_id=23"},"modified":"2026-04-03T11:26:31","modified_gmt":"2026-04-03T11:26:31","slug":"inflatable-testing-and-pipa-inspections","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.monstereventhire.co.uk\/little-monsters\/inflatable-testing-and-pipa-inspections\/","title":{"rendered":"Inflatable Inspections &#038; Pipa Testing"},"content":{"rendered":"<h1 data-section-id=\"1nviivo\" data-start=\"426\" data-end=\"488\">Inflatable Inspections &amp; PIPA Testing<\/h1>\n<p data-start=\"490\" data-end=\"646\"><strong data-start=\"490\" data-end=\"512\">Monster Event Hire<\/strong> delivers professional <strong data-start=\"535\" data-end=\"603\">inflatable inspections, PIPA inspections, and inflatable repairs<\/strong> for all types of inflatables, including:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"647\" data-end=\"768\">\n<li data-section-id=\"1lp06rv\" data-start=\"647\" data-end=\"689\"><strong data-start=\"649\" data-end=\"687\">Bouncy castles &amp; inflatable slides<\/strong><\/li>\n<li data-section-id=\"1eb0886\" data-start=\"690\" data-end=\"725\"><strong data-start=\"692\" data-end=\"723\">Obstacle courses &amp; fun runs<\/strong><\/li>\n<li data-section-id=\"j869ai\" data-start=\"726\" data-end=\"768\"><strong data-start=\"728\" data-end=\"766\">Bouncing pillows &amp; assault courses<\/strong><\/li>\n<li data-section-id=\"j869ai\" data-start=\"726\" data-end=\"768\"><strong>Bungee Runs &amp; Non ride on games<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"770\" data-end=\"937\">We are an <strong data-start=\"780\" data-end=\"824\">accredited RPII and PIPA inspection body<\/strong>, providing reliable <strong data-start=\"845\" data-end=\"871\">inflatable inspections<\/strong> to ensure your equipment meets the latest <strong data-start=\"914\" data-end=\"934\">safety standards<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"939\" data-end=\"942\" \/>\n<h2 data-section-id=\"1t8v8od\" data-start=\"944\" data-end=\"985\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.pipa.org.uk\/\">PIPA Inspections<\/a> for Inflatable Play<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"987\" data-end=\"1159\">The <strong data-start=\"991\" data-end=\"1017\">PIPA inspection scheme<\/strong> (Portable Inflatable Play Association) sets safety standards for inflatables and is supported by the <strong data-start=\"1119\" data-end=\"1156\">Health and Safety Executive (HSE)<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1161\" data-end=\"1368\">Our team performs <strong data-start=\"1179\" data-end=\"1206\">annual PIPA inspections<\/strong> for <strong data-start=\"1211\" data-end=\"1280\">bouncy castles, inflatable slides, obstacle courses, and fun runs<\/strong>, following <strong data-start=\"1292\" data-end=\"1312\">BS EN 14960:2019<\/strong>, the European standard for inflatable play equipment.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1370\" data-end=\"1567\">We carry out <strong data-start=\"1383\" data-end=\"1409\">inflatable inspections<\/strong> on-site at your venue or at our <strong data-start=\"1442\" data-end=\"1469\">Havant (Hampshire) base<\/strong>, covering <strong data-start=\"1480\" data-end=\"1513\">Hampshire, Surrey, and Sussex<\/strong>, including schools, leisure centres, and MOD sites.<\/p>\n<blockquote data-start=\"1569\" data-end=\"1637\">\n<p data-start=\"1571\" data-end=\"1637\"><strong data-start=\"1571\" data-end=\"1580\">Note:<\/strong> Full payment applies for missed appointments or slots.<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n<p data-start=\"1639\" data-end=\"1798\">We also provide <strong data-start=\"1655\" data-end=\"1685\">on-site inflatable repairs<\/strong>, including split seams, broken anchor points, or blown beds, to keep your inflatables safe and ready for play.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"1800\" data-end=\"1803\" \/>\n<h2 data-section-id=\"ktqk07\" data-start=\"1805\" data-end=\"1844\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.playinspectors.com\/\">Rpii<\/a> Operating &amp; Attendant Courses<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"1846\" data-end=\"2102\">Our <strong data-start=\"1850\" data-end=\"1866\">RPII courses<\/strong> train operators and attendants to handle inflatables safely. After completing the course, participants join the <strong data-start=\"1979\" data-end=\"2029\">RPII Register of Safe Operators and Attendants<\/strong> for 3 years, guaranteeing professional, <strong data-start=\"2070\" data-end=\"2099\">safe inflatable operation<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"2104\" data-end=\"2107\" \/>\n<h2 data-section-id=\"1mhv6k0\" data-start=\"2109\" data-end=\"2145\">Non-PIPA Inflatable Inspections<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"2147\" data-end=\"2214\">We inspect <strong data-start=\"2158\" data-end=\"2200\">non-PIPA EN14960-compliant inflatables<\/strong>, including:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2215\" data-end=\"2354\">\n<li data-section-id=\"aswix7\" data-start=\"2215\" data-end=\"2240\">Human table footballs<\/li>\n<li data-section-id=\"z31v3v\" data-start=\"2241\" data-end=\"2270\">Bungee runs &amp; eliminators<\/li>\n<li data-section-id=\"rzjmg4\" data-start=\"2271\" data-end=\"2285\">Ball pools<\/li>\n<li data-section-id=\"wldjlq\" data-start=\"2286\" data-end=\"2319\">Rodeo bulls &amp; surf simulators<\/li>\n<li data-section-id=\"g8w0zi\" data-start=\"2320\" data-end=\"2354\">Boxing rings &amp; gladiator duels<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 data-section-id=\"i7t3gc\" data-start=\"2356\" data-end=\"2384\">Bungee Run Inspections<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"2385\" data-end=\"2525\">The <strong data-start=\"2389\" data-end=\"2419\">BS EN 149604:2025 standard<\/strong> sets strict safety rules for bungee runs, covering <strong data-start=\"2471\" data-end=\"2522\">minimum height, maximum weight, and user safety<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<h3 data-section-id=\"19afuqx\" data-start=\"2527\" data-end=\"2573\">Other Non-Ride-On Inflatable Inspections<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2574\" data-end=\"2603\">We issue <strong data-start=\"2583\" data-end=\"2596\">PIPA tags<\/strong> for:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2604\" data-end=\"2695\">\n<li data-section-id=\"1odxui3\" data-start=\"2604\" data-end=\"2626\">Football shootouts<\/li>\n<li data-section-id=\"1vrtp1q\" data-start=\"2627\" data-end=\"2655\">Axe-throwing inflatables<\/li>\n<li data-section-id=\"1gosca2\" data-start=\"2656\" data-end=\"2676\">Basketball hoops<\/li>\n<li data-section-id=\"1qu6o36\" data-start=\"2677\" data-end=\"2695\">Archery ranges<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<hr data-start=\"2697\" data-end=\"2700\" \/>\n<h2 data-section-id=\"1otohng\" data-start=\"2702\" data-end=\"2734\">Bouncing Pillow Inspections<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"2736\" data-end=\"2879\">We perform <strong data-start=\"2747\" data-end=\"2778\">bouncing pillow inspections<\/strong> under <strong data-start=\"2785\" data-end=\"2807\">BS EN 14960-2:2019<\/strong>, ensuring your inflatable pillows meet <strong data-start=\"2847\" data-end=\"2876\">European safety standards<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"2881\" data-end=\"2884\" \/>\n<h2 data-section-id=\"ycwghz\" data-start=\"2886\" data-end=\"2921\">Why Choose Monster Event Hire?<\/h2>\n<ul data-start=\"2923\" data-end=\"3196\">\n<li data-section-id=\"1gci81m\" data-start=\"2923\" data-end=\"2983\">Expert <strong data-start=\"2932\" data-end=\"2958\">inflatable inspections<\/strong> &amp; <strong data-start=\"2961\" data-end=\"2981\">PIPA inspections<\/strong><\/li>\n<li data-section-id=\"mjztpv\" data-start=\"2984\" data-end=\"3023\">Fast <strong data-start=\"2991\" data-end=\"3021\">on-site inflatable repairs<\/strong><\/li>\n<li data-section-id=\"11zgrzn\" data-start=\"3024\" data-end=\"3074\">Accredited <strong data-start=\"3037\" data-end=\"3053\">RPII courses<\/strong> for safe operators<\/li>\n<li data-section-id=\"1khjkz\" data-start=\"3075\" data-end=\"3125\">Based near\u00a0<strong>Portsmouth<\/strong>\u00a0with an additional office near\u00a0<strong>Guildford<\/strong>, we carry out test and inspections across <strong>Hampshire, Surrey, Sussex, and throughout the South of England, we also travel across the UK, with lots of Clients in Wales<\/strong>.<\/li>\n<li data-section-id=\"1cr5l4o\" data-start=\"3126\" data-end=\"3196\">Keep your <strong data-start=\"3138\" data-end=\"3194\">bouncy castles, slides, and inflatables safe and fun<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<hr data-start=\"3198\" data-end=\"3201\" \/>\n<p data-start=\"3203\" data-end=\"3264\">&#x1f4de; <strong data-start=\"3206\" data-end=\"3262\">Book Your Inflatable Inspection or RPII Course Today<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"3265\" data-end=\"3321\">\n<li data-section-id=\"18dglo2\" data-start=\"3265\" data-end=\"3296\">Call <strong data-start=\"3272\" data-end=\"3280\">Dave<\/strong>: 07990 520545<\/li>\n<li data-section-id=\"ljnnuo\" data-start=\"3297\" data-end=\"3321\">Office: 01428 751925<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"3323\" data-end=\"3469\">We provide <strong data-start=\"3334\" data-end=\"3399\">inflatable inspections, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pipa.org.uk\/\">PIPA<\/a> inspections, and on-site repairs<\/strong> to ensure your inflatables stay safe, compliant, and ready for fun.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-594\" src=\"\/\/www.monstereventhire.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/10\/testing.jpg\" alt=\"testing\" width=\"600\" height=\"183\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.monstereventhire.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/10\/testing.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.monstereventhire.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/10\/testing-500x153.jpg 500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Inflatable Inspections &amp; PIPA Testing Monster Event Hire delivers professional inflatable inspections, PIPA inspections, and inflatable repairs for all types of inflatables, including: Bouncy castles &amp; inflatable slides Obstacle courses &amp; fun runs Bouncing pillows&hellip;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":6,"featured_media":583,"parent":27,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","m